on a ubuntu 22.04 online server that has qccess to internet :

mkdir ~/nginx-offline
cd ~/nginx-offline
sudo apt update
sudo apt-get --yes --download-only install nginx
 cp /var/cache/apt/archives/*.deb ~/nginx-offline/
copy to the offline server :


 scp -r /home/samira/nginx-offline/* samira@172.22.3.247:/home/samira/nginx-offline



-----------------------
on ubuntu 22.04 offline server : 


mkdir /home/samira/nginx-offline
chown samira /home/samira/nginx-offline/
sudo dpkg -i *.deb

sudo apt install ./nginx_*.deb
